**Description**
Bitcoin Text Message is a simple Web based service which offers to send SMS alerts to registered users mobile phones when the price of bitcoin changes.

**Website address**
http://www.bitcointextmessage.com/ 

**Details**
Site was launched on 23-Feburary-2013

**Current Features**
Notify user when Mt Gox exchange rate goes above a threshold.
Notify user when Mt Gox exchange rate goes below a threshold.
